Package: gptcellannotator
Title: Connect Seurat Workflows to GPT Cell Annotator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "GPT Cell Annotator",
           family = "Team",
           email = "support@gpt-cell-annotator.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides an R interface for submitting marker genes or Seurat objects
    to the GPT Cell Annotator backend. Handles REST communication, CLI offline
    fallback, validation guardrails, and visualization helpers for single-cell
    workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: Pandoc (>= 2.11), libcurl (>= 7.58), OpenSSL, C++14-capable toolchain, git
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE, roclets = c("rd", "namespace", "vignette"))
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    cli,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    purrr,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    utils
Suggests:
    covr,
    devtools,
    ggplot2,
    httptest2,
    knitr,
    lintr,
    pak,
    pkgdown,
    Seurat,
    SeuratObject,
    styler,
    testthat (>= 3.1.0),
    withr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
